{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We will share it with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Take at least part of it, of the holiday cake that we baked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are our-- our brothers, and let's hope and pray that the war will be over soon.' And the next Sunday, when the peasant again, now, Mr.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kolacz, went to church, the priest even said, 'Look, this week we had visitors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The real partisans were here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They did not plunder, they did not ask for anything, but they only said that we should be patient.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We should not denounce each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We should be happy, and that the war will be coming to an end.' This was the real partisan that was us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there for almost a half a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was already before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were liberated in January 17, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the night of the liberation were a very emotional one and a very exciting one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The area-- like I stated, it was closed already to the German border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very fierce fightings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was some trenches made around, not exactly in the village, but on the outside-- double trenches, so to say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the trenches were full of Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the night, we did not know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did not have any radios or any means that the-- that the front, so to say, that the army is five kilometers or 10 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we-- the area was very much indeed with full of partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we did not know which one is the real one, which one is the other ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was-- was an Armia Krajowa, and there was Armia Ludowa, which it means was-- one was a AK army--",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
